Package: gamCopula
Type: Package
Title: Generalized Additive Models for Bivariate Conditional Dependence Structures and Vine Copulas
Version: 0.0-1
Date: 2014-08-05
Author: Thibault Vatter
Maintainer: Thibault Vatter <thibault.vatter@gmail.com>
